ED_Title: Maintenance of international security – good-neighbourliness, stability and development in South-Eastern Europe
ED_DecisionText: At its 37th plenary meeting, on 7 December 2020, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the First Committee (A/75/393, para. 7), decided to include in the provisional agenda of its seventy-seventh session the item entitled “Maintenance of international security – good-neighbourliness, stability and development in South-Eastern Europe”.
ED_Disclaimer: The final text of this decision will be contained in document A/75/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
